claim: Patton Oswalt played Doug on The King of Queens.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Patton Peter Oswalt  (  born January 27 , 1969  )  is an American stand-up comedian , writer , actor , and voice artist , known for roles such as Spencer Olchin in the sitcom The King of Queens  (  1998 -- 2007  )  , voicing Remy in the film Ratatouille  (  2007  )  , and playing multiple identical brothers , the Koenigs , on Agents of S.H.I.E.L.D.  (  2014 -- 17  )  .
